<span id="freeTextContainer9101082360164588806">This was such a horrible book! It had potential - I kept thinking the story would come around but once I got 2/3 way through the book, I knew there was no room left for a story. I finished it anyway and was really disappointed. There is absolutely NO story. Nothing. We are introduced to this family and the other characters for no reason. It&apos;s almost like the author had great ideas for characters but couldn&apos;t come up with a story line.<br/><br/>If you&apos;ve never read Grisham and this is your first book - PLE</span>
  <span id="freeText9101082360164588806" style="display:none">This was such a horrible book! It had potential - I kept thinking the story would come around but once I got 2/3 way through the book, I knew there was no room left for a story. I finished it anyway and was really disappointed. There is absolutely NO story. Nothing. We are introduced to this family and the other characters for no reason. It's almost like the author had great ideas for characters but couldn't come up with a story line.<br /><br />If you've never read Grisham and this is your first book - PLEASE don't judge him by it. This is, by far, his worst book in my opinion.</span>
